to hire a moped for 100 Baht a day. We all shared a moped and found that life was super easy with one. Even just one of the girls stayed over so it was 3 people on a moped. Normally you would find many locals riding their bicycles or walking to the market for whatever they needed.

You can dine out for 150 Baht (all up) at a Karl’s. That will get you a pop, a meal and ice cream. (brekkie = 8 Baht. Lunch = 80 Baht

We ate a lot of ice cream. Just have a look at their menu.
